      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 341,
      "message": "why it is trying to do a fetch()?  this is typically and action started programmatically by a managing layer, for example a graceful shutdown of the process, probably shouldn't delay it in such case.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 477,
        "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
