      "file_path": "policy-endpoints/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/common/endpoints/event/comm/bus/internal/BusPublisher.java",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 189,
      "message": "Oh, what I meant is that these could be configurable externally in a configuration file.   For example see in here:\n\nhttps://git.onap.org/policy/drools-applications/tree/controlloop/common/feature-controlloop-management/src/main/feature/config/POLICY-CL-MGT-topic.properties\n\nI was thinking, there would be properties for these that we could make accessible external via configuration.   For example in the URL above:\n\ndmaap.sink.topics=POLICY-CL-MGT\ndmaap.sink.topics.POLICY-CL-MGT.servers=${envd:DMAAP_SERVERS}\ndmaap.sink.topics.POLICY-CL-MGT.https=${envd:DMAAP_HTTPS:true}\ndmaap.sink.topics.POLICY-CL-MGT.https=${envd:DMAAP_HTTPS:true}\ndmaap.sink.topics.POLICY-CL-MGT.retryBackOff=xxx                <--- **\n\nIn any case, do not worry about it for this review, could be added later.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 477,
        "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
        "username": "jhh"
      },
      "updated": "2022-09-19 19:48:55.000000000",
